{"tid":2068684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！香港再現禁歌","createTime":"2020-06-18T01:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:51:29.000Z","uid":74778,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3332b678889693c55bed7609615be4b53034d077","tid":2068684,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103338844351593/posts/196971448321665/?vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103338844351593%2Fposts%2F196971448321665%2F%3Fvh%3De&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4waZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=d28cd0b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103338844351593/posts/196971448321665/?vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n利申 平時電視播會即刻轉台，呢首聽曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb6406b094df269669c95ee5a4970a2d064da67","tid":2068684,"uid":307619,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"a347dd992ed1bbfc24803ef70f3b25208778ea3b","tid":2068684,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c333abeb79638d1ed88760f858aa897df7da7bdf","tid":2068684,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683c0b2ae6e4e92144c724b6f2ca5f7e65f08f8a","tid":2068684,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3332b678889693c55bed7609615be4b53034d077","tid":2068684,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103338844351593/posts/196971448321665/?vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103338844351593%2Fposts%2F196971448321665%2F%3Fvh%3De&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4waZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=d28cd0b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103338844351593/posts/196971448321665/?vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n利申 平時電視播會即刻轉台，呢首聽曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"good job!!!"},{"pid":"dae083f24b210133bfa0329300c28fb0118e4d55","tid":2068684,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"百分百冤獄"},{"pid":"f0751f94b31ccffee56c280b632454afb3074741","tid":2068684,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" cla